{"type":"message","id":"640bf177","parentId":"2054673a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:36:59.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了几个和生成视频相关的技能，最匹配你需求的是这几个：\n\n1. **AI Video Gen** (@qiujiahong) - 使用火山引擎 Doubao Seedance 模型，支持文生视频、图生视频、有声视频，正好符合生成视频需求 🎬\n2. **LH Video Gen** (@liuhedev) - 从 Markdown 脚本生成竖屏短视频(9:16)，生成TTS音频、渲染字幕卡片，合成MP4\n3. **AI Video Script Generator** (@aguo333) - 先根据文档内容生成完整的视频脚本，包含分镜描述、画面提示词、配音文案\n\n另外还有：\n- **Demo Video Creator - 录制产品演示视频\n- **Flyworks Avatar Video - 数字人视频生成，让图片说话\n\n最适合你需求的是第一个 `AI Video Gen`，需要火山引擎API支持直接生成视频。你想安装哪个？我帮你安装？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":6653,"output":211,"cacheRead":20280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774100215326}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"fdfba0af","parentId":"640bf177","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:37:01.045Z","summary":"## Decisions\nNo prior history.\n\n## Open TODOs\nNone.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\nNone.\n\n## Pending user asks\nNone.\n\n## Exact identifiers\nNone captured.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- No decisions have been made yet.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Search Clawhub for skills related to generating videos.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- (none)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- The user asked to search Clawhub for skills related to video generation.\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- `openclaw-control-ui` (label and id)\n- `Sat 2026-03-21 21:35 GMT+8`\n- `clawhub search video`\n- Error message: `Rate limit exceeded`\n- Exit code: `1`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Saturday, March 21st, 2026 — 9:32 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-21 13:32 UTC\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall x4]\n- Tool result (read): # SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck