eric [ref=e151]: scripts/frame.sh\n                  - generic [ref=e152]: 1.3 KB\n                - button \"SKILL.md 776 B\" [ref=e153] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - generic [ref=e154]: SKILL.md\n                  - generic [ref=e155]: 776 B\n            - generic [ref=e156]:\n              - generic [ref=e158]: Select a file\n              - generic [ref=e160]: Select a file to preview.\n      - generic [ref=e161]:\n        - heading \"Comments\" [level=2] [ref=e162]\n        - paragraph [ref=e163]: Sign in to comment.\n        - generic [ref=e165]: No comments yet.\n  - contentinfo [ref=e166]:\n    - generic [ref=e170]:\n      - text: ClawHub · An\n      - link \"OpenClaw\" [ref=e171] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: https://openclaw.ai\n      - text: project · Deployed on\n      - link \"Vercel\" [ref=e172] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: https://vercel.com\n      - text: · Powered by\n      - link \"Convex\" [ref=e173] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: https://www.convex.dev\n      - text: ·\n      - link \"Open source (MIT)\" [ref=e174] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: https://github.com/openclaw/clawhub\n      - text: ·\n      - link \"Peter Steinberger\" [ref=e175] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: https://steipete.me\n      - text: .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"dec924bf68536c29\">>>"}],"details":{"ok":true,"format":"ai","targetId":"A5AC64F95403498259A25C90E67C7DFE","url":"https://clawhub.ai/steipete/video-frames","refs":139,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"browser","kind":"snapshot","format":"ai","wrapped":true}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774100983512}}
{"type":"message","id":"e61f9f19","parentId":"88155612","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:49:50.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个 `video-frames` 技能是干什么的：\n\n**简单说：就是从视频中提取帧截图或者剪辑短片段，基于 ffmpeg 做的工具。**\n\n你可以用它：\n1. **提取单帧截图** - 从视频某个时间点取出一张图片，比如从10秒处截一张图出来\n2. **批量提取缩略图** - 可以快速查看视频内容，检查视频里有什么内容\n3. **导出短剪辑** - 从长视频中剪出一小段片段出来\n\n**常用用法：**\n- `./scripts/frame.sh video.mp4 --out frame.jpg` → 提取视频第一帧\n- `./scripts/frame.sh video.mp4 --time 00:00:10 --out frame-10s.jpg` → 在10秒处截图\n\n它是一个很实用的工具技能，不生成视频，但是帮你处理已有的视频提取图片。现在帮你安装：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ijuh4f5ha81wmmjf9i1ky93o","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace && curl -o video-frames.zip \"https://wry-manatee-359.convex.site/api/v1/download?slug=video-frames\" && unzip -o video-frames.zip -d skills/video-frames","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":24298,"output":320,"cacheRead":2872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774100983513}}
