{"type":"message","id":"b25c16eb","parentId":"92be5977","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:49:56.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **安装完成！**\n\n这个技能已经安装好了，它的功能总结：\n- ✅ 从视频提取单帧图片（第一帧或指定时间点）\n- ✅ 使用 ffmpeg 处理，速度快\n- ✅ 你刚才想要做漫画视频，正好可以用来测试提取帧之后合成视频\n\n现在你需要配置刚才安装的 `video-gen`，需要你提供火山引擎的 API Key。配置好之后就可以开始生成视频了。你有火山引擎的 API 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":27751,"output":112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27863,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774100992479}}
