{"type":"message","id":"6fd8b547","parentId":"5a13902f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:57:02.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看来网页渲染有问题，我换个思路。火山引擎 ARK 平台的 API 端点格式应该是 `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v1/chat/completions`，Doubao Seedance 也应该在这个路径下。我们试试修改端点：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_k3eyny04x0lx3yn9bvlxzihn","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen/scripts/generate_video.py","old_string":"API_KEY = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY\", \"\")\nBASE_URL = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_BASE_URL\", \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3\")","new_string":"API_KEY = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY\", \"\")\nBASE_URL = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_BASE_URL\", \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v1\")"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":5319,"output":227,"cacheRead":23864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774101418704}}
