{"type":"message","id":"396045c2","parentId":"f68b9ff1","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:57:09.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"还是 404。哦，等等！API Key 就是 API Key，而 Doubao Seedance 在火山引擎 ARK 平台是作为推理接入点来使用的，端点应该是 `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/completions`，接入点 ID 就是你给的这个 `cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400`。\n\n让我看看技能的 README 怎么说：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_y0y3rz1wydsjafbb6v0gazyf","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen/README.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":5330,"output":165,"cacheRead":24376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29871,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774101426811}}
{"type":"message","id":"fed026ef","parentId":"396045c2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:57:09.681Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_y0y3rz1wydsjafbb6v0gazyf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# video-gen\n\nAI 视频生成 Skill，基于火山引擎 Doubao Seedance 模型，支持文生视频、图生视频、有声视频。\n\n## 安装\n\n### OpenClaw\n\n```bash\n# ClawHub 安装（推荐）\nclawhub install video-gen\n\n# Git 直接安装\ncd /path/to/your/workspace/skills\ngit clone git@github.com:qiujiahong/video-gen.git video-gen\n```\n\n### Claude Code\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.claude/skills\ngit clone git@github.com:qiujiahong/video-gen.git video-gen\n```\n\n### OpenCode\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.opencode/skills\ngit clone git@github.com:qiujiahong/video-gen.git video-gen\n```\n\n## 环境变量配置\n\n使用前需配置以下环境变量：\n\n```bash\nVIDEO_GEN_API_KEY=your-volcengine-api-key\nVIDEO_GEN_BASE_URL=https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3\n```\n\n## 获取 API Key\n\n火山引擎方舟平台：https://console.volcengine.com/ark\n\n1. 注册/登录火山引擎\n2. 开通方舟大模型服务\n3. 创建 API Key\n\n## 支持的模式\n\n- 文生视频\n- 图+文生视频\n- 图生视频（Base64）\n- 有声视频-首帧\n- 有声视频-首尾帧\n- Seedance-Lite 参考图\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774101429678}}
{"type":"message","id":"70191f15","parentId":"fed026ef","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:57:17.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了！你刚才给的这个不是 API Key，这应该是模型接入点（endpoint ID），而 API Key 应该是另一个。我改一下代码，把接入点 ID 正确处理：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5l366x9dzcb09h8mte375bkp","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen/scripts/generate_video.py","old_string":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nimport time\nimport argparse\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description='Generate video using Doubao Seedance')\n    parser.add_argument('prompt', help='Text prompt for video generation')\n    parser.add_argument('--mode', default='text_to_video', \n                        choices=['text_to_video', 'image_to_video', 'image_text_to_video', \n                                 'audio_to_video', 'image_audio_to_video', 'first_frame_audio', \n                                 'first_last_frame_audio', 'seedance_lite'],\n                        help='Generation mode')\n    parser.add_argument('--image', help='Input image for image-based modes (base64 or path)')\n    parser.add_argument('--audio', help='Input audio for audio-based modes (base64 or path)')\n    parser.add_argument('--output', default='output.mp4', help='Output video file path')\n    parser.add_argument('--model', default='doubao-seedance-1.5', help='Model name')\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    API_KEY = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY\", \"\")\n    BASE_URL = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_BASE_URL\", \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v1\")\n\n    if not API_KEY:\n        print(\"ERROR: VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY environment variable is required\")\n        sys.exit(1)","new_string":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nimport time\nimport argparse\nimport base64\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description='Generate video using Doubao Seedance')\n    parser.add_argument('prompt', help='Text prompt for video generation')\n    parser.add_argument('--mode', default='text_to_video', \n                        choices=['text_to_video', 'image_to_video', 'image_text_to_video', \n                                 'audio_to_video', 'image_audio_to_video', 'first_frame_audio', \n                                 'first_last_frame_audio', 'seedance_lite'],\n                        help='Generation mode')\n    parser.add_argument('--image', help='Input image for image-based modes (base64 or path)')\n    parser.add_argument('--audio', help='Input audio for audio-based modes (base64 or path)')\n    parser.add_argument('--output', default='output.mp4', help='Output video file path')\n    parser.add_argument('--model', default='doubao-seedance-1.5', help='Model name/endpoint ID')\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    API_KEY = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY\", \"\")\n    BASE_URL = os.environ.get(\"VIDEO_GEN_BASE_URL\", \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3\")\n\n    if not API_KEY:\n        print(\"ERROR: VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY environment variable is required\")\n        sys.exit(1)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":3329,"output":759,"cacheRead":24888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774101429683}}
