{"type":"message","id":"ed5a4b8f","parentId":"82691f2f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:57:35.991Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我明白了，在火山引擎 ARK 平台：\n- **API Key** 是你在【我的账号 → API Key 管理那里生成的\n- **模型接入点** 就是你创建推理接入点后的 ID（就是你给的这个 `cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400`\n\n那你给我的是接入点ID，而我现在需要你提供真正的API Key。你能把 API Key 发给我吗？拿到后我来配置好，然后就可以开始生成视频了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":7318,"output":135,"cacheRead":23864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31317,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774101451628}}
