{"type":"message","id":"499d9703","parentId":"8c942481","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:00:54.297Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"那我直接看火山引擎文档。正确的路径应该是 `https://www.volcengine.com/docs/6678/155299/#api-%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8`，我们自己构造：\n\n对于火山引擎 ARK 平台，视频生成接入点的完整路径应该是：\n`https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/inference/endpoints/<endpoint-id>/chat/completions`\n\n我们来看看火山方舟 API 的文档：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1i82xwmwzcje9zy9mcriyodq","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.volcengine.com/docs/6471/131309"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":496,"output":169,"cacheRead":32056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32721,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774101650264}}
