{"type":"message","id":"3edd4fbf","parentId":"5c0a3bce","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:11:57.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦原来如此！ARK 平台 API Key 就是直接的 Access Key，应该不包含 `AK` 前缀，也不是 base64 编码的。让我重新组织一下：\n\n你在火山引擎控制台拿到的：\n- **Access Key ID (AK)** 就是直接一串字符\n- **Secret Access Key (SK)** 另一串字符\n\n而 ARK 的 API Key 使用的是：**AK** 就直接是 Access Key ID。你刚才给我的 `AKLTMzU3NzA3YTVmM2Y1NDZhZmJlMzM4ZDJjMzlhMTZhZTU` 这里 `AK` 是前缀，真正的 AK 是后面的 `LTMzU3NzA3YTVmM2Y1NDZhZmJlMzM4ZDJjMzlhMTZhZTU`？\n\n不对，decode 出来是乱码，说明你就是直接把 `AK`+`实际内容` 一起发给我的，我们试试看：\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ilrfbddefyqemkas5a0uhjmu","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen && export ARK_API_KEY=\"LTMzU3NzA3YTVmM2Y1NDZhZmJlMzM4ZDJjMzlhMTZhZTU\" && export ARK_ENDPOINT_ID=\"cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400\" && python3 scripts/generate_video_ark.py \"漫画风格，一个侠客在雨中的桥上行走，慢动作，古风漫画风格\" --duration 5 --aspect-ratio 16:9 2>&1","timeout":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":30727,"output":409,"cacheRead":4408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35544,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774102310610}}
