{"type":"message","id":"64f89b00","parentId":"3c2c31f4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:12:02.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"还是不对。老大，你可以打开火山引擎 ARK 控制台，在：\n\n> https://console.volcengine.com/ark/region:ark+cn-beijing/endpoint\n\n然后找到你创建的 Seedance 接入点，点进去之后页面上方会有 API 调用示例：\n\n```bash\ncurl https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $ARK_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"endpoint id here\",\n    \"messages\": [\n      {\n        \"role\": \"user\",\n        \"content\": \"你好\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }'\n```\n\n这里的 `$ARK_API_KEY` 就是你需要复制给我的 API Key，它直接在那个 curl 示例里。你可以把完整的 bearer 后面那部分内容复制给我就行，我们直接用上。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":31006,"output":215,"cacheRead":2872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34093,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774102317691}}
