ack scabbard long sword at waist, half-raised right foot, sleeves fluttering in wind, wet black hair sticking to side face, calm eyes, ink wash background, cold tone with warm yellow lantern light in distance, smooth and strong lines, raindrops with highlight, dynamic blur trailing on sword tassel and hem, solitary chivalrous atmosphere, 8k, ultra-detailed\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"id\": \"msg_02177410273077200000000000000000000ffffac1518251fcb8a\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"service_tier\": \"default\",\n  \"status\": \"completed\",\n  \"usage\": {\n    \"input_tokens\": 65,\n    \"output_tokens\": 1097,\n    \"total_tokens\": 1162,\n    \"input_tokens_details\": {\n      \"cached_tokens\": 0\n    },\n    \"output_tokens_details\": {\n      \"reasoning_tokens\": 631\n    }\n  },\n  \"caching\": {\n    \"type\": \"disabled\"\n  },\n  \"store\": true,\n  \"expire_at\": 1774361911\n}\n","name":"chmod +x"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774102745083}}
