{"type":"message","id":"69ea683f","parentId":"a2fba5e1","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:19:21.527Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_quqn03zcsr9hq3pixk6yyjlr","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"task\": \"openclaw_daily_news\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-03-21 08:00:01\",\n  \"status\": \"completed\",\n  \"instructions\": \"搜索 OpenClaw 相关最新资讯，整理并生成一篇精美的微信公众号文章。\",\n  \"steps\": [\n    \"使用 web_search 搜索 'OpenClaw' 最新资讯（近7天内）\",\n    \"筛选2-3条最有价值的新闻/动态\",\n    \"撰写一篇微信公众号风格的文章，包含：吸引人的标题、导语/摘要、正文内容、结尾总结\",\n    \"保存文章到 wechat_articles/ 目录，文件名格式：openclaw_YYYYMMDD.md\"\n  ],\n  \"style_guide\": {\n    \"tone\": \"专业但不枯燥\",\n    \"audience\": \"技术/开发者\",\n    \"length\": \"800-1500字\"\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774102761526}}
{"type":"message","id":"97ce0597","parentId":"69ea683f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:19:25.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"今天的资讯任务已经完成了，所以现在：\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK\n\n---\n\n继续我们生成视频的任务：刚才发现问题了，你当前创建的端点是普通的 `doubao-seed` 大语言模型，它只能生成文字，不能生成视频。\n\n你需要在火山方舟 ARK 控制台上：\n\n1. 点「创建推理接入点」\n2. 在模型市场中找到 **Doubao Seedance**（豆盒视频生成模型）\n3. 创建它的推理接入点\n4. 然后把这个接入点的 ID 给我，就能生成视频了！\n\n找到之后把端点ID复制给我，我们马上就能生成漫画风格视频了～"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":5661,"output":152,"cacheRead":29496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35309,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774102761529}}
